OL,7,Fwoman in.
OL,9,Fin the early hours of 10 May 2022
OL,10,Fafter she was repeatedly stabbed by
OL,11,FPablo Hoad.
OL,13,FHoad and his girlfriend had spent the
OL,14,Fevening with Shannon and a friend when
OL,15,Fan argument broke out between Shannon
OL,16,Fand Hoad.
