OL,6,FWitnesses during the trial described
OL,7,FHoad dragging Shannon into the kitchen
OL,8,Fwhere he slammed her against the
OL,9,Fworktop, stabbed her repeatedly in the
OL,10,Fhead and neck before fleeing the house.
OL,12,FFriends called for an ambulance and
OL,13,Fprovided emergency aid to Shannon, but
OL,15,FHoad fled the scene and returned to
OL,16,Fhis home and called police confessing
OL,17,Fto stabbing Shannon telling the call
OL,18,Fhandler, "I'm the perpetrator, not the
OL,19,Fvictim. I went too far."
