OL,6,FThe 28-year-old was arrested from his
OL,7,Fhome in.
OL,9,FHoad was found guilty of manslaughter
OL,10,Fin December last year and yes was
OL,11,Fsentenced to 21 years in prison on 16
OL,12,FApril 2024.
OL,14,FShannon's family described her as a
OL,15,F"daughter, sister, niece and much
OL,16,Floved by us all and all her friends.
OL,18,F"Shannon was living in Birmingham and
OL,19,Fenjoying life. Her life has now ended
OL,20,Fin the most violent way.
