OL,6,F"She was at home with her friends
OL,7,Fwhere she should have been safe but
OL,8,Fthe actions of Pablo Hoad that night
OL,9,Ftook her life and her future away.
OL,11,F"He has taken our beloved Shannon away
OL,12,Fwhen he could have just walked away
OL,13,Finstead of doing what he did.
OL,15,F"We would like to thank the police who
OL,16,Fhave worked hard to bring us to this
OL,17,Fpoint and grateful for the people who
OL,18,Ftried to help Shannon.
