OL,6,F"Our lives will never be the same
OL,7,Fwithout her and she is missed terribly
OL,8,Fby us all."
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Jim Mahon said:
OL,11,F"Hoad lost control and repeatedly
OL,12,Fstabbed Shannon and although he claims
OL,13,Fhe never meant it to get out of hand,
OL,14,Fhe never sought any help for her.
OL,15,FInstead he ran home leaving Shannon
OL,16,Ffatally injured.
OL,18,F"Shannon had many people who loved and
OL,19,Fcared for her. I hope that they can
OL,20,Ffeel some sense of justice following
OL,21,Ftoday's result at court."
